-- Russian Direct Investment Fund Hires Slizen, Kommersant Says
-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 2012-06-08T04:40:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-08/russian-direct-investment-fund-hires-slizen-kommersant-says.html
The Russian Direct Investment Fund
hired Vitaly Slizen to help the sovereign wealth private equity
vehicle source investments in information technology,  Kommersant 
reported, citing an unidentified spokeswoman for the fund.  Since 2006, Slizen has been general director of Synterra, a
Russian telecommunications operator, the report said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at 
 fconnelly@bloomberg.net  